<div id="md" style="display: none;">
<!-- markdown -->
Linux端  
安装rsync：apt-get install rsync  
创建/etc/rsyncd.conf文件并编辑  
[demoFileBackup]     #服务名称，可配置多个  
comment = public archive  
path = /var/lib/tomcat7/webapps/ROOT/WEB-INF/application/public/      #要同步文件的位置  
use chroot = yes  
max connections=10  
lock file = /var/lock/rsyncd  
read only = no  
write only = yes  
list = yes  
uid = root  
gid = nogroup  
auth users = demo                    #同步用户名  
secrets file = /etc/rsyncd.secrets   #用户名密码文件  
strict modes = yes  
hosts allow = 10.0.0.1        #允许链接的ip，可用空格隔开多个  
hosts deny = *                       #不允许的ip  
ignore errors = no  
ignore nonreadable = yes  
transfer logging = no   
timeout = 600  
refuse options = checksum dry-run  

创建密码文件  
vi /etc/rsyncd.secrets  
demo:123456

启动rsync，如果变更配置文件再执行一次  
rsync --daemon    

Windows端  
    前往https://www.itefix.net/cwrsync-get下载free版本  
    解压到D:\Program Files (x86)\cwRsync_5.5.0_x86_Free  
    环境变量path增加D:\Program Files (x86)\cwRsync_5.5.0_x86_Free\bin  
    D:\Program Files (x86)\cwRsync_5.5.0_x86_Free下新建文件rsyncd.password里面存的是密码：123456

执行同步命令，可将此命令写入.bat脚本文件用定时任务执行它  
rsync -avz --password-file="/cygdrive/d/Program Files (x86)/cwRsync_5.5.0_x86_Free/rsyncd.password" "/cygdrive/d/Program Files/tomcat7/webapps/ROOT/WEB-INF/application/public/" demo@10.0.0.2::demoFileBackup  

/cygdrive/d 为D盘  
"/cygdrive/d/Program Files/tomcat7/webapps/ROOT/WEB-INF/application/public/" 为要同步的目录  
--password-file="/cygdrive/d/Program Files (x86)/cwRsync_5.5.0_x86_Free/rsyncd.password" 为指定密码文件位置  
demo@10.0.0.2::demoFileBackup demo为同步用户名 10.0.0.2为linux主机ip demoFileBackup为服务名称
<!-- markdown end -->
</div>
<div class="entry" id="main">
<!-- content -->
<p>Linux端 <br>
安装rsync：apt-get install rsync <br>
创建/etc/rsyncd.conf文件并编辑 <br>
[demoFileBackup] &nbsp; &nbsp; #服务名称，可配置多个 <br>
comment = public archive <br>
path = /var/lib/tomcat7/webapps/ROOT/WEB-INF/application/public/ &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;#要同步文件的位置 <br>
use chroot = yes <br>
max connections=10 <br>
lock file = /var/lock/rsyncd <br>
read only = no <br>
write only = yes <br>
list = yes <br>
uid = root <br>
gid = nogroup <br>
auth users = demo &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;#同步用户名 <br>
secrets file = /etc/rsyncd.secrets &nbsp; #用户名密码文件 <br>
strict modes = yes <br>
hosts allow = 10.0.0.1 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;#允许链接的ip，可用空格隔开多个 <br>
hosts deny = * &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; #不允许的ip <br>
ignore errors = no <br>
ignore nonreadable = yes <br>
transfer logging = no&nbsp; <br>
timeout = 600 <br>
refuse options = checksum dry-run  </p>

<p>创建密码文件 <br>
vi /etc/rsyncd.secrets <br>
demo:123456</p>

<p>启动rsync，如果变更配置文件再执行一次 <br>
rsync --daemon &nbsp; &nbsp;</p>

<p>Windows端 <br>
&nbsp; &nbsp; 前往https://www.itefix.net/cwrsync-get下载free版本 <br>
&nbsp; &nbsp; 解压到D:\Program Files (x86)\cwRsync<em>5.5.0</em>x86<em>Free <br>
&nbsp; &nbsp; 环境变量path增加D:\Program Files (x86)\cwRsync</em>5.5.0<em>x86</em>Free\bin <br>
&nbsp; &nbsp; D:\Program Files (x86)\cwRsync<em>5.5.0</em>x86_Free下新建文件rsyncd.password里面存的是密码：123456</p>

<p>执行同步命令，可将此命令写入.bat脚本文件用定时任务执行它 <br>
rsync -avz --password-file="/cygdrive/d/Program Files (x86)/cwRsync<em>5.5.0</em>x86_Free/rsyncd.password" "/cygdrive/d/Program Files/tomcat7/webapps/ROOT/WEB-INF/application/public/" demo@10.0.0.2::demoFileBackup  </p>

<p>/cygdrive/d 为D盘 <br>
"/cygdrive/d/Program Files/tomcat7/webapps/ROOT/WEB-INF/application/public/" 为要同步的目录 <br>
--password-file="/cygdrive/d/Program Files (x86)/cwRsync<em>5.5.0</em>x86_Free/rsyncd.password" 为指定密码文件位置 <br>
demo@10.0.0.2::demoFileBackup demo为同步用户名 10.0.0.2为linux主机ip demoFileBackup为服务名称</p>
<!-- content end -->
